This directory is used to place the kubeconfig file for each RHEL testing.
It is mainly used by Jenkins CI.

The kubeconfig file should be placed under 'auth' directory by following hierarchy.
The <ocp-server> is the domain name of the OCP server.

env/
├── <ocp-server>
│   ├── <cluster-name>
│   │   └── auth
│   └── README
